                        |BKB--=|CKBSpecial Event - Halloween|BKB=--|WK0

Traditionally, Halloween becomes an Open PK night. In order to facilitate
this, there should be a backup made before the special boot. Then, the
following variables should be changed in /secure/include/login.h:

------

#define LOGIN_OPENPK 0

  to:

#define LOGIN_OPENPK 1

------

#define LOGIN_BANNERS STANDARD_BANNERS

  to:

#define LOGIN_BANNERS HALLOWEEN_BANNERS

------

Toys are located in /holidays/halloween/
  

